            "text": " is a marketing automation and CRM platform that handles email, SMS, and cross-channel customer journeys. It's built for teams that want enterprise-level capabilities without the enterprise-level headache (or price tag).",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Think of it as your command center: you build automations visually, segment contacts with surgical precision, send personalized emails and texts, and track everything through a built-in CRM. Over 180,000 businesses in 170+ countries use it — from solo consultants to mid-size agencies managing dozens of client accounts.",
