            "_type": "span",
            "text": "1. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Start with the pre-built recipes, then customize.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Don't build automations from a blank canvas on day one. Pick a recipe, understand the logic, then modify it to fit your workflow. This ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "tips and best practices guide",
            "marks": [
              "l6"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " has more on this approach.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "2. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Use tags aggressively, but tag with a system.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " I tag contacts based on behavior (\"clicked CTA in launch email\"), source (\"came from webinar\"), and lifecycle stage (\"repeat buyer\"). This makes segmentation instant later.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "3. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Set up site tracking immediately.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " The moment you install the tracking code, ActiveCampaign starts building a behavioral profile for each contact. The longer it runs, the smarter your automations get.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "4. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Use the CRM even if you're a solo operator.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " I resisted this at first. Big mistake. Seeing my pipeline visually — which leads are warm, which deals are stalling — changed how I prioritize my time.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "5. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Test SMS alongside email.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " The cross-channel automation logic is one of ActiveCampaign's most underrated features. Some audiences respond better to texts. Let the data tell you.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The Bottom Line",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "ActiveCampaign keeps earning its spot on my shortlist because it respects both the beginner and the power user. You can launch your first email campaign in 20 minutes, and six months later, you can build a 15-step cross-channel automation with conditional logic, lead scoring, and CRM handoff — all without switching platforms.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The new AI features, SMS upgrades, and CRM improvements make it even more capable without making it harder to use. That's rare.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
