        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What is ActiveCampaign's Active Intelligence feature?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Active Intelligence is ActiveCampaign's built-in AI layer that generates email copy, predicts optimal send times per contact, and suggests automation improvements based on your workflow performance. It's designed to cut repetitive work so you can focus on strategy.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "How much does ActiveCampaign cost?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Plans start at $1/month for small lists (under 500 contacts) and scale based on contact count and features. All plans include automation, email marketing, and CRM access. You can try it free for 14 days with no credit card.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Is ActiveCampaign good for small businesses?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes — it's one of the strongest options for small and midsize businesses. You get enterprise-level automation and CRM features at a price that scales with your list size. The pre-built automation recipes let you get value immediately without technical expertise.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Does ActiveCampaign include SMS marketing?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes. ActiveCampaign offers two-way SMS, cross-channel automations that combine email and SMS based on engagement behavior, and built-in compliance tools like opt-out management and quiet hours enforcement.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      }
